metadata.name: SkinRunners: Phoenix #1
metadata.description:
The very first Music NFT launchpad and metaverse for Rock and Metal Music Bands! Rock'n'Verse will be the meeting point of rock and metal music bands, solo artists, music lovers and fan groups from all over the world. The first project of Rock'n'Verse is coming with an exclusive NFT serie on rock concept: SkinRunners! *The person who mints the music NFT or buys it from the second hand sale can use all the traits defined in the music nft of the single: "Phoenix" in this NFT collection, unlimitedly, and can create new musical works with these traits.

This declaration was announced to the world and to the milky-way galaxy by the one and original owner of the music work, Sel√ßuk Eser, by being included in this contract.
